T1  - Economic Evaluation of Voting Power of Common Stock
AU  - LEVY, HAIM
Y1  - 1983/03/01
PY  - 1983
DA  - 1983/03/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1540-6261.1983.tb03627.x
